citation.excerpt: The model was first presented by Veličković et. al (2017, https://arxiv.org/abs/1710.10903).

description.excerpt:
This is my experimental version of the Graph Attention Network (GAT) with two improvement. 
1. I try to improve GAT with higher order interaction between nodes of the edge instead of the first order approximation used in the origin version. 
2. A minibatch training procedure is also adopted to scale GAT for large dataset.
Trial to improve graph attention network with higher order interaction and minibatch traning
